Package tech.tablesaw.columns

Interface Column

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    BooleanColumnUtils, BooleanMapUtils, CategoricalColumn, DateFilters, DateMapUtils, DateTimeMapUtils, IntConvertibleColumn, NumberFilters, NumberMapUtils, NumberPredicates, NumberReduceUtils, NumericColumn, StringFilters, StringMapUtils, StringReduceUtils, TimeFilters, TimeMapUtils
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractColumn, BooleanColumn, DateColumn, DateTimeColumn, NumberColumn, StringColumn, TimeColumn

    public interface Column
    The general interface for columns.

    Columns can either exist on their own or be a part of a table. All the data in a single column is of a particular type.
